Multiple Grammy award-winning songstress, Mariah Carey has released a new single titled “The Distance” ahead of the released of her forthcoming album, “Caution”. The vocal powerhouse diva had on Tuesday told fans that she has a surprise for them when her new album goes up for pre-order. The surprise is here and for this effort, she enlists the help of everybody’s go-to guy, Ty Dolla Sign. The mid-tempo song is modern sounding but still in Mariah Carey’s lane which sounds great in the headphones. The production comes from Skrillex, Lido and Poo Bear. Download MC’s single, “The Distance” below: